data.description: Looking for a farm house-in town?  This home is located on a quiet street, just blocks from downtown.  The location is ideal for a private home or take advantage of the R-3 zoning and bring your business dreams to life! The rear section of the home has been converted to a private apartment, with interior and exterior access, a full kitchen, living room and bedroom and is perfect for multi-generational living, a primary suite or workspace. The enormous barn/garage offers space for chickens and/or a workshop.  You'll have room for at least 4 cars! The main house radiates an old world charm, enhanced by the oak flooring and staircase. The ground level of the main home features formal living and dining room spaces with tray ceilings and tall windows. The kitchen features cork flooring, brand new appliances and table space. You will find four of the five bedrooms on the second floor of the home and with pine floors and cedar closets. The property is truly one of a kind with its antique beauty, modern conveniences and upgrades. New water heaters in 2022, on-demand tankless water heater upstairs. Three zoned central air. Gas fireplace. Custom Tile. New appliances. Updated and upgraded fuse box and electric service.
